parameters:
Hotel Staff: Ayako-san!! Your tension, the tension
in your penis has been relieved!

That's good♡♡ Just like that!! I want you to
loosen up the tension inside meee♡♡♡♡!!
The lewdness level has increased by 9...

I received 30,000 yen from the receptionist as
payment for the massage.

Hotel Staff: I'm sorry... The characteristics and
name I heard were similar, so I made a mistake...

Hehe... It's okay. I also make mistakes like that
occasionally.

Hotel Staff: Phew... I'm glad... You're a kind
person... By the way, the person scheduled for the
interview hasn't arrived yet...
Hotel Staff: ...I'm sorry, excuse me for a moment.

Hotel Staff: Hello, this is Hotel Westside...
Oh... Today's interview...

Hotel Staff: ...Uh... \. Yes... \. What?!
Canceled!!? ...I understand... Well then... Excuse
me...

Hotel Staff: Oh... Haha... We were supposed to
have an interview for the massage department, but
they canceled last minute... It's just my luck...

Hotel Staff: It would have been fine to do it on
Tuesday... Oh, sorry for the pointless chatter. I
apologize for taking up your time.

Hotel Staff: But... this is troublesome... Should
I request to repost the job opening...

This is a chance...! If I can help someone in
need, I should be able to gain their trust...!

(Hehehe, if I can gather followers in a proper
way... Rei-san will be surprised, won't she?)
...Um, if it's alright, would you like some help?

Hotel Staff: Huh? Are you sure? We would be happy
to have you, but what about your schedule, Ayako-
san...?

If it's around Tuesday, I'll be fine. Besides, I
used to work part-time at a massage parlor before,
so maybe I can be of help.

Hotel Staff: Oh, that's reliable! Please, by all
means, thank you very much!

Hotel Staff: I was worried for a moment, but
things are going well... Maybe it's because my
horoscope was ranked first this morning, haha.
